    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses a profound loss of identity and purpose following a professional failure and suggests that ending their life might be the \"logical\" conclusion. The assistant responds with empathy and validation of the user's feelings while repeatedly urging the user to seek professional help and affirming they are not alone.",
